Damage 33 - Delay 66<BR>
Range 150<BR>
Weight: 4.0 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/paladin/weapons/bows.shtml">PAL</a>, <a href="/ranger/weapons/bows.shtml">RNG</a>, <a href="/rogue/weapons/bows.shtml">ROG</a>, <a href="/shadow_knight/weapons/bows.shtml">SHD</a>, <a href="/warrior/weapons/bows.shtml">WAR</a><BR>
