<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Yes i happen to know about this lol, it is a NO DROP bow, you have to be there to get it, It drops off a 50 or 50+ named summoned creature. I doutb you'll see to many level 14-35s running around with this bow saying forget your arrows I only need normal 50 range 1 damage arrows now Muahhha! And My God man! The power and point behind a bow is the ARROW! no ones going to stop getting high damage and range arrows because of this bow, i've notcied even with a long range bow i cant shoot 50 range arrows 150 range :P So calm yourself, make me some 8 damage arrows and we can all have fun! WOWHOW! *BTW point is to make the 33 damage be higher! then 33 by getting stronger hitting arrows* Sorry if i sound fustrated or rude i'm not in a good mood today </font></td></tr></table>
